com.hazelcast.query.impl.predicates

Interface CompoundPredicate

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AndPredicate, OrPredicate

    public interface CompoundPredicate
    Interface for predicates which operate on an array of sub-predicates. Implementations of this interface must include a default no-args constructor. If a CompoundPredicate is also a VisitablePredicate, taking into account the immutability requirements for VisitablePredicates, setPredicates(Predicate[]) should throw an IllegalStateException when invoked on a CompoundStatement whose sub-predicates have already been set.
